tmxsd:menu.name: L1Menu_Collisions2015_25nsStage1_v7_uGT_v2
tmxsd:menu.comment: Implementation of L1Menu_Collisions2015_25nsStage1_v7 for uGT. Correlation conditions are implemented as placeholders.

algorithm.name: L1_SingleJetC32_NotBptxOR_BxOffset0And1
algorithm.expression: JET32[JET-ETA_CEN] AND (NOT (EXT_BPTX_plus.v0 OR EXT_BPTX_minus.v0)) AND (NOT (EXT_BPTX_plus.v0+1 OR EXT_BPTX_minus.v0+1))

algorithm.name: L1_SingleJetC20_NotBptxOR_BxOffset0And1
algorithm.expression: JET20[JET-ETA_CEN] AND (NOT (EXT_BPTX_plus.v0 OR EXT_BPTX_minus.v0)) AND (NOT (EXT_BPTX_plus.v0+1 OR EXT_BPTX_minus.v0+1))

algorithm.name: L1_TripleJet_92_76_64_VBF
algorithm.expression: comb{JET92[JET-ETA_CEN],JET76[JET-ETA_CEN],JET64[JET-ETA_CEN]} OR (comb{JET92[JET-ETA_CEN],JET76[JET-ETA_CEN]} AND JET64[JET-ETA_FWD_NEG,JET-ETA_FWD_POS]) OR (comb{JET92[JET-ETA_CEN],JET64[JET-ETA_CEN]} AND JET76[JET-ETA_FWD_NEG,JET-ETA_FWD_POS]) OR (comb{JET76[JET-ETA_CEN],JET64[JET-ETA_CEN]} AND JET92[JET-ETA_FWD_NEG,JET-ETA_FWD_POS])

algorithm.name: L1_TripleJet_84_68_48_VBF
algorithm.expression: comb{JET84[JET-ETA_CEN],JET68[JET-ETA_CEN],JET48[JET-ETA_CEN]} OR (comb{JET84[JET-ETA_CEN],JET68[JET-ETA_CEN]} AND JET48[JET-ETA_FWD_NEG,JET-ETA_FWD_POS]) OR (comb{JET84[JET-ETA_CEN],JET48[JET-ETA_CEN]} AND JET68[JET-ETA_FWD_NEG,JET-ETA_FWD_POS]) OR (comb{JET68[JET-ETA_CEN],JET48[JET-ETA_CEN]} AND JET84[JET-ETA_FWD_NEG,JET-ETA_FWD_POS])

ext_signal.name: CASTOR_HaloMuon.v0
ext_signal.description: At least 1 CASTOR phi-sector with low but constant energy deposit along z
ext_signal.label: CASTOR R GT4

ext_signal.name: CASTOR_HighJet.v0
ext_signal.description: sector energy in castor above a threshold
ext_signal.label: CASTOR R GT4

ext_signal.name: CASTOR_MediumJet.v0
ext_signal.description: sector energy in castor above a threshold but lower than CASTOR_HighJet.v0
ext_signal.label: CASTOR R GT4

ext_signal.name: HCAL_HF_MMP_or_MPP.v1
ext_signal.description: Coincidence among any wedges with at least one in HF- and at least one in HF+
ext_signal.label: HF/HO Tech.Trig

ext_signal.name: HCAL_HF_coincidence_PM.v2
ext_signal.description: Coincidence between any wedge in HF- and any wedge in HF+
ext_signal.label: HF/HO Tech.Trig

ext_signal.name: HCAL_HF_single_channel.v0
ext_signal.description: Checks for single channel energy above a threshold by using single time sample
ext_signal.label: HF/HO Tech.Trig
